  "infoTitle": "Safety & Info",
  "infoNoEmergencyTitle": "NO EMERGENCY CALL",
  "infoNoEmergencyBody": "SmartAlarm does not send any emergency signal, does not use GPS and does not call for help. The app is solely for acoustic deterrence. It makes noise to draw attention to you, nothing more.",
  "infoWhatIsTitle": "WHAT IS SMARTALARM?",
  "infoWhatIsBody": "SmartAlarm is your personal emergency alarm, always with you, ready to use instantly. With a single tap on the large red button, you trigger a loud alarm and immediately draw attention to yourself. No matter where you are: SmartAlarm reacts without delay.",
  "infoUseCasesTitle": "TYPICAL USE CASES",
  "infoUseCaseRvTitle": "Motorhome & Camping",
  "infoUseCaseRvBody": "Quickly draw attention to yourself at remote campsites or away from civilization.",
  "infoUseCaseOutdoorTitle": "Outdoor & Hiking",
  "infoUseCaseOutdoorBody": "For hikers, joggers and cyclists in remote areas, works even without mobile network coverage.",
  "infoUseCasePublicTitle": "Public Spaces",
  "infoUseCasePublicBody": "In threatening situations on the street, in public transport or on the way to school.",
  "infoUseCaseSeniorsTitle": "Seniors & Solo Travelers",
  "infoUseCaseSeniorsBody": "For people who live alone or are travelling on their own and need to quickly attract help.",
  "infoHowItWorksTitle": "HOW IT WORKS",
  "infoHowTriggerTitle": "Trigger alarm",
  "infoHowTriggerBody": "Tap the large red button on the main screen. The alarm starts immediately at maximum volume.",
  "infoHowVolumeTitle": "Volume & Vibration",
  "infoHowVolumeBody": "The alarm plays at maximum volume. Vibration can be turned on or off in the settings.",
  "infoHowSoundTitle": "Choose alarm sound",
  "infoHowSoundBody": "Choose between siren, dog barking or your own audio file (MP3, WAV, OGG, M4A).",
  "infoHowStopTitle": "Stop alarm",
  "infoHowStopBody": "Tap \"Stop alarm\" on the alarm screen to deactivate the alarm.",
  "infoWhyOfflineTitle": "WHY NO INTERNET CONNECTION?",
  "infoWhyOfflineBody": "SmartAlarm was deliberately designed without network functionality. This has several advantages: The app works everywhere, even without Wi-Fi or mobile data, in basements, mountain huts or abroad. No data is sent or received. And there is no dependency on servers or services that could fail.\n\nThe strength of the app lies in its simplicity: one tap, instant alarm.",
  "infoPrivacyTitle": "PRIVACY",
  "infoPrivacyBody": "SmartAlarm does not collect any personal data, requires no internet connection and sends nothing externally. All settings remain exclusively on your device.",
